snippet.title: Minecraft Dungeons Diaries: Origins
snippet.description:
Minecraft Dungeons is a new action-adventure game set in the Minecraft Universe. But why does it exist? Who is making it? And exactly how much fun will it be? Learn the answers to some of those questions in this video.

Minecraft Dungeons is inspired by classic dungeon crawlers! Up to four friends can play together, or you can brave the dungeons alone. Battle new-and-nasty mobs across action-packed, treasure-stuffed, wildly varied levels, all in an epic quest to defeat the evil Arch-Illager!
